- The miracle child.

129
00:09:45.961 --> 00:09:49.715
What are you doing here? Don't you
have some scrolls to read or something?

130
00:09:49.798 --> 00:09:51.758
<i>Here. let me do that.

131
00:09:51.842 --> 00:09:55.262
Wait. wait!
You have to be very careful.

132
00:09:55.345 --> 00:09:58.056
- You might cut your hands on the soft fur.
- Get away!

133
00:09:58.140 --> 00:10:01.727
- I-- I just want to help.

134
