You've helped enough. Thanks to you.
we'll work an extra hour today.

135
00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:08.650
You're not tired because you got up early.
It's because you were out all night.

136
00:10:08.734 --> 00:10:11.153
Why. you little sneak.

137
00:10:11.236 --> 00:10:15.449
What do you know? I know about everything
the women and the drinking.

138
00:10:15.532 --> 00:10:18.577
- There's a lot Father doesn't know.
- You wouldn't.

139
00:10:18.660 --> 00:10:20.579
- He would. The little brat.
- Aah!

140
00:10:20.662 --> 00:10:23.916
If you say one word. I'll wring
your skinny neck.  Stop it!

141
00:10:23.999 --> 00:10:26.877
If Father sent him.
we should be happy for his help.

142
00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:30.339
Maybe he can do your work. Simeon.
Huh! Somebody should.

143
00:10:30.422 --> 00:10:34.301
Besides. there is something
Joseph can do.

144
00:10:34.384 --> 00:10:37.596
<i>What's he doing? I don't know.
Shh!

145
00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:41.433
While we round up the strays.
can you watch the herd for us?

146
00:10:41.517 --> 00:10:43.727
- Of course.
- Good.

147
00:10:43.810 --> 00:10:47.022
We'll be back soon.
Let's go.

148
00:10:47.105 --> 00:10:49.691
Maybe we should split up.
You go over there.

149
00:10:49.775 --> 00:10:53.445
- <i>I'll go this way.
- Hey! What are you doing? Hey!

150
00:11:08.836 --> 00:11:11.046
