What?

154
00:11:30.148 --> 00:11:33.068
Are you making fun of me too?

155
00:11:38.407 --> 00:11:41.410
Hey!

156
00:11:41.493 --> 00:11:43.912
Hey. come back!

157
00:11:46.540 --> 00:11:48.625
Huh?

158
00:11:54.339 --> 00:11:56.300
Get away!
Get away!

159
00:12:04.057 --> 00:12:06.727
Gotcha!

160
00:12:18.363 --> 00:12:20.449
Back! Back!

161
00:12:20.532 --> 00:12:23.744
Get away!

162
