164
00:12:36.006 --> 00:12:38.926
Your brothers. where are they?

165
00:12:39.009 --> 00:12:42.095
I asked you a question!

166
00:12:42.179 --> 00:12:45.057
They're--
They're. uh--

167
00:12:45.140 --> 00:12:47.809
They--
They went swimming.

168
00:12:47.893 --> 00:12:50.646
Swimming?

169
00:12:50.729 --> 00:12:54.066
- What happened?
- This is how you take charge?

170
00:12:54.149 --> 00:12:57.611
I expect you to watch afterJoseph.
but you abandoned my son.

171
