- Come on.Joseph. Tell us.

191
00:14:51.934 --> 00:14:54.686
<i>We're dying to hear about it.

192
00:14:54.770 --> 00:14:57.356
All of us were carrying
sheaves of wheat.

193
00:14:57.439 --> 00:15:01.109
I was among you.
but then all of a sudden.

194
00:15:01.193 --> 00:15:03.737
I was above you
and your wheat bowed to me--

195
