but there could be a message here.

202
00:15:33.016 --> 00:15:36.687
Judah's led the herd for years.
brought in the wheat. raised the tents.

203
00:15:36.728 --> 00:15:40.732
He comes first before any of us.
especiallyJoseph.

204
00:15:40.816 --> 00:15:44.069
<i>Judah. it's not up to me.

205
00:15:44.152 --> 00:15:47.072
God may be telling us
something of our future.

206
00:15:47.155 --> 00:15:50.075
