Apologize to each other!

213
00:16:10.554 --> 00:16:12.639
Let me talk toJoseph.

214
00:16:18.562 --> 00:16:21.481
<i>He's just a boy.
You're too harsh on him.

215
00:16:21.565 --> 00:16:24.151
You're always defending him!

216
00:16:24.568 --> 00:16:27.237
