than you are.

221
00:16:43.086 --> 00:16:46.006
We're family. all of us.

222
00:16:47.758 --> 00:16:50.969
If we break apart.
we have nothing left.

223
00:16:53.931 --> 00:16:58.143
# You've seen the damage
words can do #

224
00:16:58.227 --> 00:17:01.605
- This is God's plan.
-<i># When full of thoughtless pride #

225
00:17:01.647 --> 00:17:04.191
That's enough!

226
00:17:04.274 --> 00:17:08.278
# Now heed the wiser voice in you #

227
00:17:08.362 --> 00:17:13.200
