494
00:37:02.139 --> 00:37:05.142
I did nothing wrong.

495
00:37:05.184 --> 00:37:08.312
<i>Yeah. we know you're innocent.

496
00:37:31.543 --> 00:37:35.380
<i>I know it sounds crazy.
but it was so real.

497
00:37:35.422 --> 00:37:40.636
I was up all night with
my own dreams. Now you wanna
take up my day with yours?

498
00:37:40.719 --> 00:37:44.848
<i>No.Just listen.
I was back at Pharaoh's palace...

499
00:37:44.890 --> 00:37:49.144
