What can be done?

631
00:50:13.138 --> 00:50:16.308
<i>You must find a man you can trust.

632
00:50:16.391 --> 00:50:20.187
During the years of plenty. have him
collect one-fifth of the grain...

633
00:50:20.270 --> 00:50:23.524
