636
00:50:32.324 --> 00:50:35.994
With my life. Excellency.

637
00:50:44.086 --> 00:50:47.464
Through this man.
I have seen the future of Egypt.

638
00:50:49.633 --> 00:50:53.470
<i>And through his deeds.
we shall prosper.

639
